      "width": 420,
      "height": 260,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Dynamic Render Modes\n\nThis class defines multiple node-view payload modes directly on the class artifact:\n\n- dyn-md -> render.markdown\n- dyn-html -> render.html\n- dyn-text -> render.text\n- dyn-json -> render.json\n\nEach view now declares `view.renderShape` so content kind and source path are explicit.\n\nIt now resolves as a self-describing class graph without a local dictionary.",
